model.gizmos

Interface IGizmo

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Absorber, Circle, Flipper, Gizmo, LeftFlipper, RightFlipper, Square, Triangle

    public interface IGizmo
    The gizmo interface The gizmo interface provides public access to useful methods for the gizmos
